<chapter label="16" id="adv-wm-xresources">

<title>X Resources</title>

<para>
It is possible to put X resources in xfwmrc. They are commands starting 
with a "*". This can be especially usefull for customizing xfpager. For 
example:
</para>

<programlisting>
*xfpager.geometry -0+0
*xfpager.smallfont 5x8
</programlisting>

</chapter>
